You know how I was.

352
00:18:38,485 --> 00:18:40,702
How you doing these days?

353
00:18:40,737 --> 00:18:43,121
Feeling like I crawled out
from the bottom of a bottle

354
00:18:43,156 --> 00:18:45,540
