about that night at the bar?

369
00:19:20,777 --> 00:19:23,111
Uh, did you talk to
Hoffman or Fensky at all?

370
00:19:23,163 --> 00:19:27,332
Sorry. I got nothing.
They weren't my people.

371
00:19:27,367 --> 00:19:29,534
