374
00:19:34,374 --> 00:19:36,341
We're done here, yeah.

375
00:19:36,376 --> 00:19:38,176
Hey, that wasn't so hard, huh?

376
00:19:38,211 --> 00:19:39,177
Thanks, Mike. Yeah.

377
00:19:39,212 --> 00:19:40,628
Listen, we're probably

378
