413
00:21:13,556 --> 00:21:16,357
Yep. [Sighs]

414
00:22:02,196 --> 00:22:03,464
[sighs]

415
00:22:03,495 --> 00:22:04,744
[Dialing]

416
00:22:11,105 --> 00:22:13,489
Yeah, it's me.

